The paper deals with the problem of image analysis and retrieval, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of multiple feature sets and the integration of multi-view information is also a common theme in multimedia analysis (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the proposed algorithm involves graph-based methods, which are often used in social network analysis (cs.SI).
